<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | Essence</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/styles.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Montserrat:wght@200;300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Fix for Our Values circles */
        .value-icon-fixed {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .value-circle-fixed {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: var(--pink-light);
        }
        
        /* Fix header spacing on mobile */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .about-hero {
                padding-top: 100px;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .about-hero {
                padding-top: 80px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="about-page">
    <div class="cursor"></div>
    <div class="page-transition"></div>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">IVORY BEAUTY</div>
        <div class="search-container">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Search products..." class="search-input">
            <button class="search-btn">
                <span class="search-icon">&#9906;</span>
            </button>
        </div>
        <nav class="desktop-nav">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/" class="active">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/products">Products</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div class="header-icons">
            <div class="auth-icons">
                <a href="/login" class="icon-btn" aria-label="Sign in">
                    <i class="fas fa-user icon"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="cart-icon">
                <a href="/cart" class="icon-btn" aria-label="Shopping cart">
                    <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart icon"></i>
                    <span class="cart-count"><%= cartCount %></span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hamburger-menu">
            <div class="bar"></div>
            <div class="bar"></div>
            <div class="bar"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mobile-nav">
            <div class="mobile-nav-header">
                <div class="logo">IVORY BEAUTY</div>
                <div class="close-menu">Ã—</div>
            </div>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/" class="active">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="/products">Products</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mobile-nav-footer">
                <div class="mobile-search">
                    <input type="text" placeholder="Search products..." class="search-input">
                    <button class="search-btn">
                        <span class="search-icon">&#9906;</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="mobile-actions">
                    <a href="/login" class="btn-outline">Sign In</a>
                    <a href="/signup" class="btn">Sign Up</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="about-hero" style="padding-top: 80px;">
            <div class="about-hero-content">
                <h1 class="fade-in">Our <span class="highlight">Story</span></h1>
                <p class="fade-in delay-1">Founded on the belief that beauty thrives in simplicity</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-hero-image fade-in delay-2">
                <div class="image-container"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mission">
            <div class="mission-content reveal">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>At IVORY BEAUTY, we believe that skincare should be a celebration of your natural beauty, not a complex regimen of countless products. Our mission is to create simple, effective formulations that work in harmony with your skin's natural processes.</p>
                <p>We strip away the unnecessary and focus on what truly matters: quality ingredients, thoughtful formulations, and results you can see and feel.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="founders">
            <div class="founders-image reveal">
                <div class="image-container"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="founders-content reveal delay-1">
                <h2>The Founders</h2>
                <p>IVORY BEAUTY was born from a shared vision between two friends, Claire and Sophia, who were frustrated by the overwhelming complexity of modern skincare.</p>
                <p>With backgrounds in cosmetic chemistry and holistic wellness, they set out to create a line that embodied their belief that beauty thrives in simplicity.</p>
                <p>Five years later, their vision has grown into a collection that has helped thousands rediscover the joy of simple, effective skincare.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="values">
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Our Values</h2>
            <div class="values-container">
                <div class="value-item reveal">
                    <!-- Fixed circle container -->
                    <div class="value-icon-fixed">
                        <div class="value-circle-fixed"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Simplicity</h3>
                    <p>We believe in doing more with less. Our formulations focus on essential ingredients that deliver real results.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-item reveal delay-1">
                    <div class="value-icon-fixed">
                        <div class="value-circle-fixed"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Transparency</h3>
                    <p>We're committed to clear, honest communication about our ingredients, sourcing, and manufacturing processes.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="value-item reveal delay-2">
                    <div class="value-icon-fixed">
                        <div class="value-circle-fixed"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                    <p>Our commitment to simplicity extends to our environmental impact, with mindful packaging and responsible sourcing.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="process">
            <div class="process-content reveal">
                <h2>Our Process</h2>
                <p>Every IVORY BEAUTY product begins with a question: What does your skin truly need? From there, we work with leading formulators to create products that deliver those benefits with minimal ingredients.</p>
                <p>We test extensively, refine continuously, and only release products that meet our exacting standards for efficacy and experience.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="process-image reveal delay-1">
                <div class="image-container"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="team">
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Meet Our Team</h2>
            <div class="team-container">
                <div class="team-member reveal">
                    <div class="member-image">
                        <div class="hover-reveal"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Claire Bennett</h3>
                    <p>Co-Founder & Formulator</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member reveal delay-1">
                    <div class="member-image">
                        <div class="hover-reveal"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Sophia Lin</h3>
                    <p>Co-Founder & Creative Director</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member reveal delay-2">
                    <div class="member-image">
                        <div class="hover-reveal"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3>James Wilson</h3>
                    <p>Head of Product Development</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="join-us">
            <div class="join-us-content reveal">
                <h2>Join Our Journey</h2>
                <p>We're always looking for passionate individuals who share our vision of beauty in simplicity.</p>
                <button class="btn">View Opportunities</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <div class="footer-logo">IVORY BEAUTY</div>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4>Shop</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/products">All Products</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Bestsellers</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/products">New Arrivals</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Gift Sets</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4>About</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/about">Our Story</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Ingredients</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Sustainability</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Blog</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h4>Help</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="#">Contact Us</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Shipping & Returns</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">FAQ</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#">Track Order</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-social">
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ivorybeautyempire?igsh=MW9hM3MybDc1bG50cw=="" class="social-icon"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon"><i class="fab fa-pinterest"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; 2025 IVORY BEAUTY. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script src="../js/animations.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
